5-14T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"ok 喎, 咬字清晰無懶音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢已經接左job 錄vo<br />\n<br />\n「借錢梗要還 咪俾錢中介」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得報稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551cb9ab21bee3a4ded4d9cf1cc96a1f69fbaa96","tid":1154592,"uid":12949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"樓主教人用老翻 + 裝毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/jailbreak-iphone-poisoning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fjailbreak-iphone-poisoning&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=8eda2f69\" target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/jailbreak-iphone-poisoning</a><br />\n<br />\n少數用戶都喜愛安裝非來自 App Store 版本的 App，像是大陸地區的XX助手商店，上面提供了海量破解免費 iPA 資源，有的更會標示「無需越獄」就能高速下載使用，不過大家有想過為什麼他們這麼樂於免費提供這些？是否曾聽過一句話叫做「免費的最貴」經典名言呢？直接套用在這上面就相當適合。<br />\n<br />\n假如一款原本可正常從 App Store 下載的免費 App ，跟透過這些助手商店上下載會有什麼差異？<br />\n<br />\n如助手的開發者在 App 內「加料」後，並且放上這些非官方管道的商店上，提供用戶安裝 App 時，某些原本 App 不該出現的檔案，當用戶安裝時，就會直接順勢裝入至原本不該裝的位置上，那會導致什麼樣的後果呢？當然就是可以訪問並且收集設備內的資訊，像是簡訊內容、電話、支付寶、QQ、微信、LINE、FB 等裡面用戶資料，甚至還會被植入廣告和其它無法曝光的用途，就讓各位自行想像。"},{"pid":"da9db44300e3db1d1d3ec17384f17ed3a6a160fe","tid":1154592,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c60d10b1884ceb4283e677a6351f735a19bf0114","tid":1154592,"uid":62204,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3dfa8e62e962a613717deacdbed3be769c803165","tid":1154592,"uid":72228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母把死人聲咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:33:08.000Z","msg":"又關你事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f225934c068cc3e3d1dac6e1ac0a7a78ade465b0","tid":1154592,"uid":62204,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":